{
  "stem": "5470.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "For that reason, they sent them over to Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And after the war, he was liberated there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he organized the back transport of all the other Dutch people who are still living in that township back to Holland.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And his daughter, she was in-- also a lawyer.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was a lawyer and her daughter, too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That-- well, that's the question where I come to.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So in August 1945, I went with the last transport-- but because my promise was I bring the Jewish people back into their own community afterwards.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was my instruction, and I wanted to finish that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that was the last transport back home for these people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I went with them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And went over then to Rotterdam, where my wife's parents lived.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But from there on, I visited quite a number of, of people whom I knew in the camp.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I saw first then [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Kerido, ?] and he was working in the hospital.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was a doctor.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Later on, he became professor.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we had a chat there together about all things.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He said, do you still want to see my uncle, Professor [?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Myers? ?] I said, yes, because he was living opposite the hospital.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So together, we went over to the other side of the road.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that's where we had a chat together.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And before I left, I said to him, tell me, Professor, what was now the main reason why you didn't want to go out of, out of the camp when I asked you?",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He said, well-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I'm a very well-known person in the country.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So many more people know me than I know them.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
